Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and Real Housewives of New York. On RHOBH, the women get their charts read, the group continues to turn on Kyle, plus Mr. Girardi acts! On RHONY, the women go to a spa and Dorinda confronts her behavior-ish.


RHONY Recap: 25:14ish
